plstart:

Synopsis: Create a plot-window.

Syntax: plstart ( NCOL , NROW , DEVICE )

Description:

	Create a plot-window. The newly created plot-window becomes
	the current plot-window with NCOLxNROW sub-plots. DEVICE
	specifies the output device type. If DEVICE is not specified,
	then the default of "/XWIN" is used (if this isn't suitable
	for your system, then edit rlib/plot.r).
